    Grafana sends HTTP requests to Prometheus endpoints, specifying the desired metrics and time ranges.
    Prometheus processes these queries, retrieves the relevant data from its time-series database, and returns the results to Grafana. 
    Grafana then visualizes this data in dashboards, allowing users to monitor and analyze system performance in real-time.
23. What is PromQL?
